result.formatted_address: Tat Tung Rd, Tung Chung, Hong Kong
result.name: Midam Korean Restaurant

reviews.text:
Very good experience.. very nice staff.
Food very good. i recommend this hidden restaurant located behind the cable car station. Not crowded, very convenient to avoid all the people and queue from the Citygate Outlet restaurant.
The price is reasonable compare to the quality of the food.
Authentic korean food.
Korean BBQ is available of course.
reasonable price and the food is authentic
Yummy Bbq rib

A rather quiet place. I like it. Slightly away from the main crowd of Tung Chung vicinity. Price is quite good too. I didn't know there was a restaurant here as one cannot really see it from the main street and the signboard is not strategically located. Probably it is better this way for the customers though, as everywhere else in Tung Chung is so crowded.
Great bargain for the good quality and spacious environment for group gatherings!
